269
00:20:28,490 --> 00:20:30,149
Excuse me,

270
00:20:30,149 --> 00:20:32,809
who is getting married today?

271
00:20:32,809 --> 00:20:36,810
- Leader Liu.
- Oh! Leader Liu?

272
00:20:36,810 --> 00:20:38,400
Leader Xi Gua is so young and capable.

273
00:20:38,409 --> 00:20:42,329
She must be married to someone as young and capable.

274
00:20:42,329 --> 00:20:46,969
Can you tell me who she is marrying?

275
00:20:46,969 --> 00:20:48,790
Our counselor.

276
00:20:48,790 --> 00:20:49,649
Good.

277
00:20:49,649 --> 00:20:51,889
It's good to marry a counselor.

278
00:20:54,469 --> 00:20:56,349
Isn't your counselor

279
00:20:56,349 --> 00:20:57,708
Ning Yi?

280
00:20:57,709 --> 00:20:58,809
Yes.

281
00:20:58,809 --> 00:21:01,469
Liu Xi Gua is marrying Ning Yi?

282
00:21:02,290 --> 00:21:03,709
But Ning Yi is my nephew-in-law!

283
00:21:03,709 --> 00:21:04,630
My cousin-in-law!

284
00:21:04,630 --> 00:21:06,830
How can they get married?

285
00:21:06,830 --> 00:21:08,869
No. No. Let me tell you! I don't agree!

286
00:21:08,870 --> 00:21:11,150
I don't agree, either!

287
00:21:11,870 --> 00:21:14,789
So, you are the family of our counselor.

288
00:21:14,789 --> 00:21:15,809
What a coincidence.

289
00:21:15,809 --> 00:21:19,930
Holy Master ordered that anyone who hinders the marriage

290
00:21:19,930 --> 00:21:22,210
shall be killed.

291
00:21:25,950 --> 00:21:27,609
This is such a good event.

292
00:21:27,609 --> 00:21:30,389
I will see who dares to disagree with it.

293
00:21:30,389 --> 00:21:32,709
Yes. They are born to marry each other.

294
00:21:32,709 --> 00:21:35,169
They will live happily forever. They will have their babies soon.

295
00:21:35,169 --> 00:21:36,329
Happy wedding!

296
00:21:36,329 --> 00:21:38,089
Treasures will fill your home

297
00:21:38,089 --> 00:21:41,029
- Amitabha.
- Amitabha.

298
00:21:41,029 --> 00:21:44,250
Get out of my face. Get your asses out of here!

299
00:21:45,269 --> 00:21:46,769
Leave now.

300
00:21:47,390 --> 00:21:49,010
Hurry up!

301
00:21:49,010 --> 00:21:51,150
This way. This way!

302
00:21:53,000 --> 00:21:53,820
[Fang Manor]

303
00:21:53,820 --> 00:21:56,029
How can you ask him to marry me so easily?

304
00:21:56,029 --> 00:21:57,229
I don't want to get married.

305
00:21:57,229 --> 00:21:59,630
How can you control our lives?

306
00:21:59,630 --> 00:22:01,269
You like him, don't you?

307
00:22:01,269 --> 00:22:03,290
Of course, I should help you.

308
00:22:03,290 --> 00:22:05,350
Why should I marry him if I like him?

309
00:22:05,350 --> 00:22:07,349
I have never thought like that.

310
00:22:07,349 --> 00:22:10,748
In the hall, you said you liked him in front of so many people.

311
00:22:10,749 --> 00:22:12,249
So he has to marry you.

312
00:22:12,249 --> 00:22:15,649
I promised your late father that I will make you happy.

313
00:22:15,649 --> 00:22:17,749
Aunt,

314
00:22:17,749 --> 00:22:20,370
Xi Gua said she's unwilling to do so.

315
00:22:20,370 --> 00:22:22,930
Chen Fan, give me a break.

316
00:22:22,930 --> 00:22:25,129
Xi Gua can marry someone she likes.

317
00:22:25,129 --> 00:22:26,370
What's bad about it?

318
00:22:26,370 --> 00:22:29,570
This is my own life. Don't force me.

319
00:22:29,570 --> 00:22:34,210
Xi Gua, this is not your own business now.

320
00:22:34,210 --> 00:22:37,649
If only you didn't say you liked him.

321
00:22:37,649 --> 00:22:41,050
Yet you said it and it happened in front of so many people.

322
00:22:41,050 --> 00:22:44,050
You are the leader of Badao Camp.

323
00:22:44,050 --> 00:22:45,989
You can't even marry him?

324
00:22:45,989 --> 00:22:47,890
You would lose your face.

325
00:22:47,890 --> 00:22:49,369
You would embarrass the whole Badao Camp.

326
00:22:49,369 --> 00:22:52,790
How would people see you? How would they see Badao Camp?

327
00:22:54,329 --> 00:22:56,870
I don't mind it at all.

328
00:22:57,409 --> 00:22:59,709
What? You–

329
00:23:01,809 --> 00:23:03,309
Fine.

330
00:23:03,930 --> 00:23:05,409
You won't marry him, right?

331
00:23:05,409 --> 00:23:07,670
Think about it well.

332
00:23:07,670 --> 00:23:12,369
You should know what would happen since Ning Yi killed Bao Wenhan.

333
00:23:12,889 --> 00:23:16,470
Everyone in the eight camps wants to take his life now.

334
00:23:16,470 --> 00:23:20,770
If he marries you, nobody will dare to lay a finger on him.

335
00:23:20,770 --> 00:23:22,850
If you don't marry him,

336
00:23:22,850 --> 00:23:27,390
Xuanwei Camp won't let him get away with it and you know it well.

337
00:23:27,390 --> 00:23:30,309
If he is caught by them,

338
00:23:30,309 --> 00:23:32,309
I can't guarantee he will stay safe.

339
00:23:32,309 --> 00:23:35,210
So, Xi Gua, I won't force you.

340
00:23:35,210 --> 00:23:37,970
You decide whether you'll marry or not.

341
00:23:37,970 --> 00:23:40,050
Master, Ning Yi has been married.

342
00:23:40,050 --> 00:23:42,210
You both know it.

343
00:23:44,129 --> 00:23:46,890
He is just a matrilocal husband.

344
00:23:46,890 --> 00:23:49,290
We can force him to divorce.

345
00:23:51,290 --> 00:23:52,990
But…

346
00:23:56,550 --> 00:23:59,990
But… Ning Yi and his wife love each other.

347
00:23:59,990 --> 00:24:02,029
I don't want to break up a family.

348
00:24:02,029 --> 00:24:03,889
He can love his wife.

349
00:24:03,889 --> 00:24:06,089
Then he can also fall in love with you, too.

350
00:24:06,089 --> 00:24:08,050
You should be more confident.

351
00:24:08,050 --> 00:24:12,050
And if he marries you, he has to divorce his wife.

352
00:24:12,050 --> 00:24:15,110
You can't share a husband with another woman.

353
00:24:21,490 --> 00:24:26,790
- Xi Gua!
- This kid has been spoiled by us.

354
00:25:07,050 --> 00:25:08,550
Master,

355
00:25:08,550 --> 00:25:12,730
how about the situation in the Secret Investigation Department?

356
00:25:16,329 --> 00:25:18,529
After the sneak attack,

357
00:25:18,529 --> 00:25:20,570
we lost half of our people.

358
00:25:20,570 --> 00:25:22,789
We need some time to recover.

359
00:25:22,789 --> 00:25:26,850
But we only have three days left.

360
00:25:26,850 --> 00:25:28,089
The attack failed.

361
00:25:28,089 --> 00:25:30,169
I guess the powder may have been transferred.

362
00:25:30,169 --> 00:25:33,869
We don't have enough people in the city to cooperate with Dong.

363
00:25:33,870 --> 00:25:37,250
It seems we have to make an opportunity

364
00:25:37,250 --> 00:25:41,790
to attack them when they have a weak defense.

365
00:25:43,649 --> 00:25:45,330
I understand.

366
00:25:47,649 --> 00:25:53,749
And please report to Right Chancellor Qin.

367
00:25:53,749 --> 00:25:57,370
Also tell him not to worry too much.

368
00:25:57,370 --> 00:25:59,209
I will think of a solution

369
00:26:01,169 --> 00:26:03,229
to get back Lin'an.

370
00:26:08,490 --> 00:26:10,090
Ning Yi.

371
00:26:13,809 --> 00:26:16,150
Ning Yi, you are here.

372
00:26:16,150 --> 00:26:19,150
I have been looking for you. I have something important to tell you.

373
00:26:19,210 --> 00:26:20,490
What's wrong?

374
00:26:20,490 --> 00:26:23,390
I can't refuse our marriage.

375
00:26:25,649 --> 00:26:27,830
We killed Bao Wen Han.

376
00:26:27,830 --> 00:26:30,570
It would not be easy for them to forget it.

377
00:26:30,570 --> 00:26:32,509
You knew it.

378
00:26:34,609 --> 00:26:36,329
If they make it difficult for your family,

379
00:26:36,329 --> 00:26:37,970
I will send them out of the city first.

380
00:26:37,970 --> 00:26:41,290
When it's all over, we will get back to what we are. Your wife will still be your wife.

381
00:26:41,290 --> 00:26:43,530
All things happening here won't be effective.

382
00:26:43,530 --> 00:26:46,169
Let's find a way to help you survive.

383
00:26:46,169 --> 00:26:47,490
Thank you.

384
00:26:47,490 --> 00:26:48,889
It's nothing.

385
00:26:48,889 --> 00:26:50,770
Explain it clearly to your wife.

386
00:26:50,770 --> 00:26:53,609
The reason why I said I like….

387
00:27:00,129 --> 00:27:03,309
I said that nonsense

388
00:27:03,309 --> 00:27:05,950
in order to protect you.

389
00:27:08,530 --> 00:27:10,270
It's a deal.

390
00:27:10,270 --> 00:27:11,849
Talk to your wife about this.

391
00:27:11,849 --> 00:27:13,930
Ask her not to take it seriously.

392
00:27:13,930 --> 00:27:15,210
I'm leaving now.

393
00:27:15,210 --> 00:27:16,810
Liu Xi Gua.

394
00:27:19,530 --> 00:27:20,770
What's wrong?

395
00:27:20,770 --> 00:27:22,490
You are being wordy.

396
00:27:29,809 --> 00:27:31,630
I'm sorry.

397
00:27:31,630 --> 00:27:33,789
Sorry for what?

398
00:27:34,369 --> 00:27:36,950
You are my friend! You owe me this!

399
00:28:34,649 --> 00:28:35,649
My dear.

400
00:28:35,649 --> 00:28:37,509
Where have you been?

401
00:28:40,089 --> 00:28:41,129
I had a meeting.

402
00:28:41,129 --> 00:28:42,670
Tell me the truth.

403
00:28:42,670 --> 00:28:44,509
I went to drink.

404
00:28:46,690 --> 00:28:52,209
I heard Young Master Ning will marry Leader Liu in Badao Camp.

405
00:28:52,209 --> 00:28:54,129
I should send my congratulations.

406
00:28:54,129 --> 00:28:56,010
A big wedding is coming.

407
00:28:56,010 --> 00:29:00,650
Do you want to divorce your wife

408
00:29:00,650 --> 00:29:03,890
or make her your concubine?

409
00:29:03,890 --> 00:29:05,670
Stand there!

410
00:29:05,670 --> 00:29:07,389
Are you allowed to come?

411
00:29:07,389 --> 00:29:10,548
- It was all fake. It was all fake!
- Say it louder!

412
00:29:11,169 --> 00:29:15,069
It's just a show. It's fake!

413
00:29:15,110 --> 00:29:17,310
Fake?

414
00:29:18,369 --> 00:29:20,810
And you agreed! Didn't you?

415
00:29:20,810 --> 00:29:22,649
No, no, my dear.

416
00:29:22,649 --> 00:29:24,249
Kneel down!

417
00:29:26,229 --> 00:29:28,689
Don't. It's quite dangerous...

418
00:29:30,369 --> 00:29:33,490
We actually have a plan.

419
00:29:33,490 --> 00:29:35,329
What plan?

420
00:29:36,469 --> 00:29:39,089
I dare not say it since you're pointing scissors at me.

421
00:29:39,089 --> 00:29:40,290
Well, I will stop teasing you.

422
00:29:40,290 --> 00:29:42,050
Hubby, what is your plan?

423
00:29:42,050 --> 00:29:43,089
Tell me.

424
00:29:43,089 --> 00:29:45,390
You scared me to death!

425
00:29:47,369 --> 00:29:50,149
We do have a plan.

426
00:29:50,149 --> 00:29:54,830
But you have to cooperate with us.

427
00:29:55,730 --> 00:29:57,789
Now I have to cooperate.

428
00:29:57,789 --> 00:30:02,870
That is to say, I have to help you marry another lady. Right?

429
00:30:02,870 --> 00:30:07,830
Young Master Ning, you look like an honest man

430
00:30:07,830 --> 00:30:12,210
but you do know how to enjoy yourself by having two wives.

431
00:30:12,210 --> 00:30:13,810
No.

432
00:30:13,810 --> 00:30:15,710
Did I allow you to come?

433
00:30:15,710 --> 00:30:16,970
Sit back.

434
00:30:16,970 --> 00:30:19,490
Fine, I will.

435
00:30:20,649 --> 00:30:22,249
Say it.

436
00:30:29,170 --> 00:30:30,809
Nephew-in-law! Nephew-in-law!

437
00:30:30,809 --> 00:30:32,809
I have been looking for you.

438
00:30:32,809 --> 00:30:34,490
Come. Come.

439
00:30:34,490 --> 00:30:36,708
I have something important to tell you.

440
00:30:36,709 --> 00:30:37,609
Stop.

441
00:30:37,609 --> 00:30:39,708
It can't be more important than mine.

442
00:30:39,709 --> 00:30:41,409
I have…

443
00:30:41,970 --> 00:30:43,169
You might no longer be my cousin-in-law.

444
00:30:43,169 --> 00:30:44,210
Isn't that important?

445
00:30:44,210 --> 00:30:45,390
Yes.

446
00:30:45,390 --> 00:30:48,010
Tan'er, you know about his coming wedding.

447
00:30:48,010 --> 00:30:49,250
What are you going to do?

448
00:30:49,250 --> 00:30:52,230
How dare a matrilocal husband marry another lady?

449
00:30:52,230 --> 00:30:54,609
This is really immoral.

450
00:30:54,609 --> 00:30:55,849
Nobody can stand it.

451
00:30:55,849 --> 00:30:57,569
If it is known by people in Jiangning,

452
00:30:57,569 --> 00:31:00,010
- our grandfather will be pissed off.
- Yeah.

453
00:31:00,010 --> 00:31:03,450
Uncle, we already have a plan to cope with the wedding.

454
00:31:03,450 --> 00:31:04,908
Don't worry.

455
00:31:04,909 --> 00:31:06,509
We still have something to do. We've got to go.

456
00:31:06,509 --> 00:31:07,969
Let's go.

457
00:31:07,969 --> 00:31:09,408
Hey, Tan'er. Tan'er!

458
00:31:09,408 --> 00:31:10,250
Ning Yi.

459
00:31:10,250 --> 00:31:11,850
Cousin-in-law.

460
00:31:13,469 --> 00:31:14,290
Father.

461
00:31:14,290 --> 00:31:16,990
Tan'er knew Ning Yi would marry another girl.

462
00:31:16,990 --> 00:31:18,690
Has she gone crazy or just lost her soul?

463
00:31:18,690 --> 00:31:21,809
She didn't cry or make a fuss about it but she smiled.

464
00:31:21,809 --> 00:31:25,029
Since when did young people become this open now?

465
00:31:25,029 --> 00:31:26,468
We can't let it happen.

466
00:31:26,469 --> 00:31:27,468
I will have to ask her again.

467
00:31:27,469 --> 00:31:29,209
Come back! Come back.

468
00:31:30,490 --> 00:31:33,690
Wen Xing, think about it.

469
00:31:33,690 --> 00:31:37,330
If Ning Yi marries Liu Xi Gua,

470
00:31:37,330 --> 00:31:39,729
then he'll be dumped by the Su Family.

471
00:31:39,729 --> 00:31:41,710
Tan'er has to divorce him anyway.

472
00:31:41,710 --> 00:31:45,569
Without Ning Yi,

473
00:31:45,569 --> 00:31:49,210
can Tan'er still manage the family business?

474
00:31:51,189 --> 00:31:53,669
You mean… In this way,

475
00:31:53,669 --> 00:31:57,609
the property of the Su Family will belong to us.

476
00:31:58,469 --> 00:32:02,010
This couple has contributed a lot to our family.

477
00:32:02,010 --> 00:32:05,549
But who would know we'll get their fruits?

478
00:32:06,550 --> 00:32:09,789
Then we will be the richest people in Jiangning.

479
00:32:09,790 --> 00:32:11,950
Lay low.

480
00:32:11,950 --> 00:32:14,490
I'm so happy to even think about it.

481
00:32:17,450 --> 00:32:19,870
What you said is right.

482
00:32:22,169 --> 00:32:24,789
But how can we get back to Jiangning?

483
00:32:27,390 --> 00:32:29,810
I know nothing good will happen to us.

484
00:32:39,010 --> 00:32:40,690
It is so strange.

485
00:32:40,690 --> 00:32:42,468
There used to be a house.

486
00:32:42,469 --> 00:32:44,190
Now it is gone.

487
00:32:47,770 --> 00:32:49,570
Forget it.

488
00:32:49,570 --> 00:32:52,530
You four build a house here for me.

489
00:32:52,530 --> 00:32:53,609
I don't need a fancy one or anything.

490
00:32:53,609 --> 00:32:54,350
I just want a house that will accommodate

491
00:32:54,351 --> 00:32:55,589
more than ten people and not collapse.

492
00:32:55,590 --> 00:32:56,789
I want to see it by tomorrow.

493
00:32:56,790 --> 00:32:57,869
Tomorrow?

494
00:32:57,870 --> 00:33:00,610
That's too hasty.

495
00:33:00,610 --> 00:33:02,249
What?

496
00:33:03,229 --> 00:33:05,710
You all have become lazy in the city.

497
00:33:05,710 --> 00:33:09,050
Back when we were in the mountains, you could build one in half a day.

498
00:33:09,050 --> 00:33:09,990
Hurry up!

499
00:33:09,990 --> 00:33:11,990
- Yes.
- Yes.
- Yes.

500
00:33:13,010 --> 00:33:15,290
Why are you building a house?

501
00:33:25,889 --> 00:33:27,489
Master.

502
00:33:36,369 --> 00:33:38,269
Master. Madame.

503
00:33:38,269 --> 00:33:41,808
- I knew that Chen Fan is in love with Xi Ggua.
 - Master, let me out!

504
00:33:41,808 --> 00:33:42,730
Yes.

505
00:33:42,730 --> 00:33:43,951
We have watched him grow up.

506
00:33:43,951 --> 00:33:45,370
- Madame! 
- I know him so well.

507
00:33:45,370 --> 00:33:48,109
- Leader Fang. 
- But they don't match each other.

508
00:33:48,110 --> 00:33:50,250
They both like to fight with their swords.

509
00:33:50,250 --> 00:33:51,950
- If they get married—
- Xi Gua can't get married!

510
00:33:51,950 --> 00:33:53,869
- How can they live peacefully? 
- She can't!

511
00:33:53,870 --> 00:33:55,349
- Lock him here first. 
- Master!!

512
00:33:55,350 --> 00:33:57,210
- In case he causes any trouble on her wedding.
- Master!

513
00:33:57,210 --> 00:33:59,950
After the wedding, we will free him.

514
00:34:12,109 --> 00:34:14,250
Put it over there.

515
00:34:14,250 --> 00:34:16,410
What has Ning Yi been doing these days?

516
00:34:16,410 --> 00:34:17,390
Nothing special.

517
00:34:17,390 --> 00:34:20,410
- He sent his wife to Lou's Cloth Store.
- Slow down.

518
00:34:20,410 --> 00:34:22,589
He should be back by now.

519
00:34:22,589 --> 00:34:26,869
After his wedding with Xi Gua, don't let him meet his ex-wife.

520
00:34:26,869 --> 00:34:29,930
- And don't invite his family here.
- I think it's good.

521
00:34:29,930 --> 00:34:31,889
I will go to check on Xi Gua.

522
00:34:31,889 --> 00:34:33,909
Send our invitations to all the camps. Don't miss any camps.

523
00:34:33,909 --> 00:34:36,049
- Yes.
 - Put it over there. Hurry up!

524
00:34:37,490 --> 00:34:40,790
Erhei, make sure the flag is in place. Set it well.

525
00:34:40,810 --> 00:34:42,110
Okay.

526
00:34:50,970 --> 00:34:53,129
Stop what you're doing for a while.

527
00:34:53,129 --> 00:34:54,929
Come here.

528
00:35:00,089 --> 00:35:02,828
Now, there is an urgent task for us.

529
00:35:02,829 --> 00:35:04,890
- Okay.
- No problem!

530
00:35:06,089 --> 00:35:07,249
Drink more.

531
00:35:07,249 --> 00:35:09,230
Come on. Drink more.

532
00:35:12,530 --> 00:35:14,490
Why are you so late?

533
00:35:16,050 --> 00:35:17,010
Buddy. Buddy.

534
00:35:17,010 --> 00:35:18,828
May I ask you… if...

535
00:35:18,828 --> 00:35:20,268
This is the wedding invitation of

536
00:35:20,269 --> 00:35:22,469
- Leader Liu and our Young Master?
- Yes.

537
00:35:22,469 --> 00:35:24,450
Are we invited?

538
00:35:24,450 --> 00:35:26,209
- No.
- No?

539
00:35:26,209 --> 00:35:29,330
My nephew-in-law is marrying again but you don't even invite us?

540
00:35:29,330 --> 00:35:31,490
We are the richest people in Jiangning.

541
00:35:31,490 --> 00:35:32,788
But the truth is you are not invited.

542
00:35:32,789 --> 00:35:34,130
Why?

543
00:35:34,130 --> 00:35:35,809
Is there a problem?

544
00:35:36,910 --> 00:35:38,629
Any problem?

545
00:35:38,630 --> 00:35:41,329
No. No. No.

546
00:35:41,329 --> 00:35:44,228
After all, we are relatives of Tan'er.

547
00:35:44,229 --> 00:35:46,209
They are afraid that we may cause trouble.

548
00:35:46,209 --> 00:35:47,950
- I can understand.
- I understand.

549
00:35:47,950 --> 00:35:49,109
Father, don't worry, don't worry.

550
00:35:49,110 --> 00:35:52,308
If they don't invite us, we will go eat something even better.

551
00:35:52,309 --> 00:35:54,888
- Of course!
- I'll leave you alone.

552
00:35:59,609 --> 00:36:01,129
We have sent the invitations to all eight camps

553
00:36:01,129 --> 00:36:02,050
and not one is missed.

554
00:36:02,050 --> 00:36:02,930
I know that.

555
00:36:02,930 --> 00:36:05,030
You can go now.

556
00:36:11,050 --> 00:36:14,469
Aunt, it's just a wedding.

557
00:36:14,469 --> 00:36:16,909
We don't have to invite that many people.

558
00:36:16,909 --> 00:36:18,429
You have no idea.

559
00:36:18,430 --> 00:36:22,389
Since it is your wedding ceremony, we have to make it big.

560
00:36:22,389 --> 00:36:24,289
It's troublesome.

561
00:36:24,289 --> 00:36:26,350
You are going to get married.

562
00:36:26,350 --> 00:36:29,689
Don't carry your sword all day.

563
00:36:31,289 --> 00:36:33,969
I'm used to it.

564
00:36:33,969 --> 00:36:34,910
I know you so well.

565
00:36:34,911 --> 00:36:36,330
When you have something on your mind,

566
00:36:36,330 --> 00:36:38,169
you like to play with your sword.

567
00:36:38,169 --> 00:36:39,669
What?

568
00:36:39,669 --> 00:36:41,569
Are you are getting nervous?

569
00:36:44,169 --> 00:36:46,189
There is no need to be nervous.

570
00:36:46,189 --> 00:36:48,610
Although we forced him to marry you,

571
00:36:48,610 --> 00:36:49,970
we are all chivalrous people.

572
00:36:49,970 --> 00:36:51,689
We never cared about these trivial manners.

573
00:36:51,689 --> 00:36:54,450
After your wedding, if you get along well with him,

574
00:36:54,450 --> 00:36:56,589
he will fall in love with you.

575
00:36:56,589 --> 00:36:58,809
You are such a beautiful girl.

576
00:36:58,809 --> 00:37:01,189
So many guys want to marry you.

577
00:37:01,189 --> 00:37:03,650
Ning Yi is so lucky to have you.

578
00:37:03,650 --> 00:37:05,710
Nonsense.

579
00:37:05,710 --> 00:37:07,869
Between him and I…

580
00:37:11,630 --> 00:37:12,748
Well, enough.

581
00:37:12,749 --> 00:37:14,090
I will stop.

582
00:37:14,090 --> 00:37:16,629
You have to get prepared now.

583
00:37:17,490 --> 00:37:18,450
I know.

584
00:37:18,450 --> 00:37:19,890
Aunt, please go back first.

585
00:37:19,890 --> 00:37:22,110
Please leave me alone.

586
00:37:22,110 --> 00:37:23,828
All right.

587
00:37:23,829 --> 00:37:26,210
I will go. I will.

588
00:37:29,229 --> 00:37:32,310
Have a rest early tonight.

589
00:37:32,310 --> 00:37:34,390
I know that.

590
00:37:58,890 --> 00:38:00,490
Father,

591
00:38:03,729 --> 00:38:05,790
I'm getting married

592
00:38:06,930 --> 00:38:09,590
tomorrow.

593
00:38:41,769 --> 00:38:43,369
Father,

594
00:38:43,970 --> 00:38:49,529
thank you for taking care of me all the way along.

595
00:38:49,529 --> 00:38:51,989
You are my son.

596
00:38:51,989 --> 00:38:55,089
Don't say things like that.

597
00:38:55,810 --> 00:38:59,930
Although it was a tough journey,

598
00:38:59,930 --> 00:39:04,449
we got good results in the end.

599
00:39:04,449 --> 00:39:06,009
Yes.

600
00:39:06,009 --> 00:39:08,429
We have worked hard for half of our lives

601
00:39:08,429 --> 00:39:11,669
and finally, become rich merchants.

602
00:39:11,669 --> 00:39:14,790
Yet we can't even

603
00:39:14,790 --> 00:39:19,450
spend our money in the city during the lockdown.

604
00:39:20,129 --> 00:39:22,189
Why?

605
00:39:24,510 --> 00:39:26,810
My son.

606
00:39:26,810 --> 00:39:32,250
This is the so-called destiny.

607
00:39:35,129 --> 00:39:37,269
Father, look.

608
00:39:38,689 --> 00:39:41,329
We finally have somewhere to spend our money.

609
00:39:41,329 --> 00:39:43,249
Welcome. Steamed buns that just came out.

610
00:39:43,249 --> 00:39:45,330
- Do you want one?
- I will buy two.

611
00:39:45,330 --> 00:39:47,670
What? Two? That's not enough.

612
00:39:47,670 --> 00:39:49,689
How many people do you have in your family?

613
00:39:49,689 --> 00:39:50,689
Fifteen, please.

614
00:39:50,689 --> 00:39:52,389
Okay.

615
00:39:54,250 --> 00:39:56,450
Please. 30 cash in total.

616
00:39:56,450 --> 00:39:57,290
Give me your address.

617
00:39:57,290 --> 00:39:58,729
I will send the money to your house later.

618
00:39:58,729 --> 00:39:59,609
Hold on.

619
00:39:59,609 --> 00:40:01,748
You want me to give you credit even when buying some steamed buns?

620
00:40:01,749 --> 00:40:03,669
Are you crazy because of poverty?

621
00:40:03,669 --> 00:40:04,890
Poverty?

622
00:40:04,890 --> 00:40:05,890
I am not afraid to tell you.

623
00:40:05,890 --> 00:40:09,430
We are the householders of the Su Family,

624
00:40:09,430 --> 00:40:10,748
the richest family in Jiangning.

625
00:40:10,749 --> 00:40:13,169
Have you heard of us? You must be afraid now.

626
00:40:13,169 --> 00:40:14,970
We are just stuck in Lin'an now.

627
00:40:14,970 --> 00:40:17,890
When we go back to Jiangning, we can even buy your stand,

628
00:40:17,890 --> 00:40:19,729
