629
00:40:19,729 --> 00:40:21,269
It's no big deal to us.

630
00:40:21,269 --> 00:40:26,149
If you want to have a store, we can open one for you.

631
00:40:26,149 --> 00:40:27,909
You can choose the location.

632
00:40:27,910 --> 00:40:30,069
At that time, you won't have to work so hard

633
00:40:30,070 --> 00:40:33,550
